parameters.content: Call Gateway that obtains inbound call data from vapi.ai platform.
Generates an entry in Airtable's 'Call Logs' table with conversation specifics
Validation Check that returns true when legitimate call information is captured from the API endpoint.
Verifies if the conversation was successfully completed/incomplete according to termination code.
Queries Airtable database for prospect entries corresponding to the contact's telephone identifier.
Modifies the prospect status in Airtable to 'Called' following a completed conversation.
Increases the contact try count for the prospect in Airtable prior to initiating subsequent outreach
Fetches the lead's profile from Airtable using the contact's telephone identifier as search key.
Accesses the prospect data when contact tries surpass the established limit.
Adjusts the prospect status in Airtable to 'Failed' following maximum allowed outreach efforts.
Populates the explanation field with 'Unreachable' for unsuccessful communication efforts.
Changes the lead status in Airtable to 'TBC' from a human representative.
Verifies if the outreach attempt tally remains under the maximum limit of 2.
Introduces workflow delay of one minute before continuing sequence.
Initiates system API call to commence additional outreach to the identical prospect.
Dispatches a concise email notification to the prospect's email containing information about upcoming follow-up.
Delivers a brief notification email to the prospect's contact address informing them of upcoming follow-up.

parameters.subject: Thank You for Our Recent Call - Interia Design Follow-up
parameters.message:
=Dear {{ $json.fields['FirstName'] }},

Thank you for contacting us about Interia's interior design services. We had a wonderful conversation and appreciated learning about your needs. Our team will be following up with you soon to continue our discussion about your project.
Warm regards,
The Interia Team
